answer_llm:
Because Azure OpenAI expects the tool schema to include a `function` object inside each tool entry. The error means your tool definition is missing that required structure.

Use this format for `get_weather_tool`:

```json
get_weather_tool = {
    "type": "function",
    "function": {
        "name": "get_weather",
        "description": "Get the current weather for a specific city or generate fake data",
        "parameters": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
                "city": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "description": "The name of the city to get the weather for."
                }
            },
            "required": ["city"],
            "additionalProperties": false
        }
    }
}
```

If you want, I can also help you convert your current tool definition into the correct Azure OpenAI format.

